{"tid":1557136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方、消防、醫管局、港鐵就 8.31 晚事件　十二時半會見傳媒","createTime":"2019-09-10T03:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:56:36.000Z","uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdf05b207dc29455f3d98a207f46f4e7739102a","tid":1557136,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"警務處警察公共關係科高級警司余鎧均及消防處高級助理救護總長羅信堂今日（九月十日）下午十二時三十分就八月三十一日晚上在港鐵站內發生的事件會見傳媒。醫院管理局高級行政經理龔澤民及香港鐵路有限公司車務營運總監黃琨暐亦會出席。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n生要見人 死要見屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5ed1af951b248e738975409c2a6749857d496b","tid":1557136,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"消防兩次點算的傷者數目不同，到場後初步點算為 <span style=\"color: red;\">10 人</span>，最終 <span style=\"color: red;\">7 人</span>送院<br />\n<br />\n位置四：22 : 57 太子站底層月台 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">往中環</span></strong>車廂<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內</span></span></strong><br />\n急救期間，列車突然一搖、開出，時為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23 : 03</strong></span>分。<br />\n<br />\n位置七：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23 : 00 </strong></span>太子站底層月台 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>往中環</strong></span>第 5 卡至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>車尾</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3 分鐘後</span></strong>，往中環列車開出；再過 2、3 分鐘往調景嶺列車亦開出，同時警方開始驅趕月台上所有記者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23:03 match 23:00+3mins</strong></span><br />\n<strong>所以係有可能有人見到，係22:57 - 23:03 之間，共6分鐘</strong><br />\n<br />\n位置六：23 : 07 太子站底層月台 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">往中環</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車頭</span></span></strong>對出<br />\n他記得被捕者一排排地蹲下，堆了至少三排、近 60 人；然後左方有一位昏迷不醒的黑衣男子，驟眼看沒有血，不知如何弄成這樣。有一個軍綠色 T 恤的男子則被打得頭破血流，還有一個「肥仔」好像恐慌症發作，一度手腳僵直呼吸困難。 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共三人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「你問我覺得有無死人？我不能排除這個可能。」David說，「因為我親眼見過有人不省人事，連同那軍綠色衫的男仔，事後在警署都沒碰過面了。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n剩下的事情，只有警方、港鐵職員、消防救護員及被捕者知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1556113/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1556113/page/1</a><br />\n【專題】地圖重組 8.31太子站 閉路電視有真相嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-8-31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%97%8E/?fbclid=IwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2597%258E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD6mkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=fe5d5615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2597%258E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds&h=72fdfbfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-8-31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%89%